law.text: All registration records of the Transportation Cabinet made or kept pursuant to the issuance of a certificate of number shall be public records.
law.history: Amended 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 391, sec. 12, effective July 13, 1990. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 263, sec. 11, effective June 17, 1978. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 292, sec. 12. -- Created 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 68, Art. VIII, sec. 16, effective March 17, 1960.
